DJ Info;

Born in the heart of Amsterdam and welknown throughout the Netherlands, Dj Spider is well in demand, 
playing all the big clubs in the Netherlands. Spider is well known for his outstanding technical capabilities.
 
With his mix of trance, groove and techtrance he takes you on Ã¢â‚¬Å“a trip through a world of dreamsÃ¢â‚¬ï¿½. 
In no-time his blend of grooves and rhythms, combined with an energetic stage performance, creates a real party-atmosphere amongst the crowd.
 
Apart from performing on stage Spider is also an avid organiser, throwing some of the biggest parties in 
Amsterdam like Full Moon and Xtra Large.

These two cd's are some of his work in the late 90's but still very great to listen (especially
